{"tid":420912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左重需要人明咩","createTime":"2017-10-01T18:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T07:54:23.000Z","uid":150425,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"20d35c08ce355b2367c5aa905eadc31afa887b0a","tid":420912,"uid":150425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:46:36.000Z","msg":"以前細個有心事有煩腦<br />\n總會搵三五密友訴苦<br />\n但係人大左 煩惱越黎越多<br />\n開始覺得麻木<br />\n唔係覺得同人地講左人地唔會明自己<br />\n而係有時連自己愁乜都唔係太清楚<br />\n又或者覺得講左出黎都唔會解決到<br />\n所以寧願將心事收翻係心底..<br />\n人大左重需要人明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae49d751826c311a3d056343d07ed71a0be93421","tid":420912,"uid":22888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:48:33.000Z","msg":"需要"},{"pid":"6c8f197ae4c622d718a5d702ebaef092a436a1a2","tid":420912,"uid":146924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:50:19.000Z","msg":"有咩事唔好收收埋埋 有個人傾訴下點都好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4006b090c546b8949b9ec39ab1bef5fe322d7720","tid":420912,"uid":110112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:52:00.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n而且講完俾佢地知<br />\n佢地又會講出去"},{"pid":"f4cab891f1f699d5c31aeb995fbeb17793309fa7","tid":420912,"uid":150425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係<br />\n而且講完俾佢地知<br />\n佢地又會講出去</blockquote><br />\n所以你好需要私穩政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcde0e5c4d48f7de4a80b57dd78c003d7d0ab73d","tid":420912,"uid":86791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T19:25:38.000Z","msg":"重乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78943a06a7322090e2026854866a67084f8dd8f0","tid":420912,"uid":146924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T22:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個先係正字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991cd6c42fbd8f4760d5fde1981249d53d189950","tid":420912,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T22:16:44.000Z","msg":"We're born alone, we live alone, we die alone"},{"pid":"c2d86c1af9e4a6a77cbfb70680d7c653183c1b96","tid":420912,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T22:24:09.000Z","msg":"如果唔需要嘅，你打上黎做乜<br />\n你唔需要人明白，但需要人認同??<br />\n人地唔明白你，又點會認同你?<br />\n所以你根本需要人明白，講到唔需要咁"},{"pid":"7853a435a963af3a96b9878b0aa460bdaf6eb987","tid":420912,"uid":150425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻鳩正字都唔撚識"},{"pid":"ac7746a021be86759bbf58bfe98864e1d2a2bed5","tid":420912,"uid":143306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:07:58.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同人訴苦都要解釋一大輪，講完佢又唔明，明左佢又幫我唔到。"},{"pid":"8d9fe7180be92c171437822a5a3b7190dc69642d","tid":420912,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:09:35.000Z","msg":"變左惡性循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19def8a183c77d24e4d8e4a50fb99b5a7294b529","tid":420912,"uid":14333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"大概是老大了<br />\n自己亦懂得 心裡有病 暗地治療<br />\n不替友伴 製造著煩擾"},{"pid":"f836fb83b508a30604dc6dbf24957acc68f4e5e0","tid":420912,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"做慣聆聽者 自己好少將私事同人地講"},{"pid":"39a85893f8100a610c5e21802a6ec995ac2ddd9c","tid":420912,"uid":48680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:54:23.000Z","msg":"需要既<br />\n搵既過程太痛苦姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}